    "en": {
      "title": "Greetings to the President from Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma, who ran as a candidate for the parliamentary presidential election, says that he congratulates the new president from the bottom of his heart.",
        "Mr. Alahapperuma, who claims that his political ideology was not defeated by numbers, says that the reason is because he represented 225 people in Diwannawe Island and 58 lakh people outside of Nuwata Island. Mr. Alahapperuma also says that he would like to express his respectful thanks to all the parties and members who believed in him.",
        "Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma mentions this in a post on his Facebook account."
      ],
